Label: util_TNC Shared_switch
Description: TNC Shared - switch turn-off (depends on data availability)

Label: util_TNC_SHARED_cost
Expression: @df.coef_cost * np.where(df.nev_available, nevCost, np.where(df.microtransit_available, microtransitCost, (np.maximum(TNC_shared_baseFare + (df.s3_dist_skims * TNC_shared_costPerMile) + (df.s3_time_skims * TNC_shared_costPerMinute), TNC_shared_costMinimum))) * 100 + df.s3_cost_skims)

Label: util_WALK_LOC_Walk_egress_time
Expression: @np.where(df.nev_local_egress_available_out & df.outbound, df.nev_local_egress_time_out, np.where(df.microtransit_local_egress_available_out & df.outbound, df.microtransit_local_egress_time_out, df.dest_local_time)) * df.time_factor

Label: util_WALK_PRM_In_vehicle_time_on_LTD_EXP
Description: WALK_PRM - In-vehicle time on LTD and EXP

Label: util_WALK_PRM_Walk_egress_time
Expression: @np.where(df.nev_prm_egress_available_out & df.outbound, df.nev_prm_egress_time_out, np.where(df.microtransit_prm_egress_available_out & df.outbound, df.microtransit_prm_egress_time_out, df.dest_prm_time)) * df.time_factor

Label: util_WALK_PRM_wait_egress_time
Expression: @1.5 * np.where(df.nev_prm_egress_available_out & df.outbound, nevWaitTime, np.where(df.microtransit_prm_egress_available_out & df.outbound, microtransitWaitTime, 0)) * df.time_factor

Label: util_WALK_MIX_In_vehicle_time_on_LTD_EXP
Description: WALK_MIX - In-vehicle time on LTD and EXP

Label: util_WALK_MIX_Walk_egress_time
Expression: @np.where(df.nev_mix_egress_available_out & df.outbound, df.nev_mix_egress_time_out, np.where(df.microtransit_mix_egress_available_out & df.outbound, df.microtransit_mix_egress_time_out, df.dest_mix_time)) * df.time_factor

Label: util_WALK_MIX_wait_egress_time
Expression: @1.5 * np.where(df.nev_mix_egress_available_out & df.outbound, nevWaitTime, np.where(df.microtransit_mix_egress_available_out & df.outbound, microtransitWaitTime, 0)) * df.time_factor
